text: Maxime Cam (born 9 July 1992) is a French professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI ProTeam . ==Major results== ;2010 : 2nd Ronde des Vallées ;2014 : 5th Overall Kreiz Breizh Elites ;2017 : 5th Overall Tour de Bretagne Cycliste : 6th Paris–Chauny ;2019 : 3rd Overall Kreiz Breizh Elites ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:French male cyclists Category:People from Landerneau Category:Sportspeople from Finistère
title: Maxime Cam
